data.description: Beautiful New Construction Home! This elegant open concept home features 3 bedrooms + den and 2 bathrooms. Too many upgrades to list: 42” solid wood white cabinets, luxurious quartz countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, impact windows, stainless steel appliances, HUGE master shower with frameless glass door, tile floors throughout, tray ceilings in great room and Master bedroom, 8 foot tall doors, 6” base boards, 10 foot ceilings throughout with 11 foot vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting and asphalt poured driveway. Home will be ready July 2021. Still in time to pick some finishes. Photos are of a similar home and may not be an exact representation of the home being built as products and specifications may be changed.
